A mimic sculpt in Zbrush that was made for a Halloween projection show on the the library at Chatham University. The primary purpose of this model is to look good when rendered. This was originally rendered in Unreal Engine 5 but was revised and re-rendered in Marmoset Toolbag 5. The backdrop was also made in marvelous designer.

